    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "At 6:45 AM this date, SAC Hood telephonically contacted the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Bureau and advised at approximately 11:30 PM, July 9, 1947, the office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "in Los Angeles had received information from the Resident Agent at Burbank,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "California, that a \"flying disc\" had landed in or near Burbank and had been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "seen to burst into flame when it landed. Further, that it had been the cause",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "of a fire in some woods, this fire either in Burbank or possibly in the city",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "limits of Los Angeles, which Mr. Hood could not be certain. The fire chief",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "at Burbank had called the resident agent at Burbank and told him he would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "hold the disc for him.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "67c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Coincident with the information received from Burbank, the Los Angeles",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Office received calls from the newspapers requesting information. The newspapers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "stating they had called the Army Air Force Intelligence who had stated \"we are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "not interested\". According to Mr. Hood, this comment had aroused the newspapers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "and they stated they intended to publish this quotation and belabor same in their",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "first issues. Mr. Hood stated that he had refrained from making any statement",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "to the press other than to admit possession of an object and that it was being",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "turned over to military authorities in the morning (this AM), it being Mr. Hood's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "opinion that he did not want any quotes in the press and certainly not one to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "effect that we were not interested.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "As described to him, Mr. Hood stated that the object was an aluminum",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "disc about 2' in diameter weighing about ten pounds, painted with aluminum paint,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "and having some sort of a radio tube in the center of the disc. This object was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "in possession of the resident agent at Burbank and would be turned over to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "military authorities (G-2) in Los Angeles this morning.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "67c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "RECORDED",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "Mr. Hood's purpose in calling was to place the Bureau on notice regarding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "the above described object and any further information would be transmitted to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "Bureau at once.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "FX-53",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "Action: None indicated.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
